dct_title_s: Watling Island, to accompany Mr. Major's paper
dct_description_sm: Depth shown by soundings and isobaths. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Location of anchorage of Columbus on October 12, 1492 is shown. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 41 (1871), pp. 193-210; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v. 4 1834
